<section id="citation-standards" class="provenance-record" aria-labelledby="citation-heading">
  <div class="section-inner provenance-grid">
    <header>
      <p class="section-label">05</p>
      <h2 id="citation-heading">Citation Standards</h2>
    </header>
    <div>
      <p>Each AI-generated or AI-assisted work identifies its classification, Matthew's final editorial authority, the role of ATLAS, the role of ChatGPT or Codex when applicable, the work's title and date, and the source material from which it was prepared.</p>
      <p><strong>ATLAS Report form:</strong> Matthew Taylor Marx, director and editor. “Title.” ATLAS Report, generated with ATLAS through OpenAI ChatGPT; repository publication assisted by OpenAI Codex. Forgotten Industries, YYYY-MM-DD.</p>
      <p><strong>Curated entry form:</strong> Matthew Taylor Marx, author and editor. “Title.” AI-assisted editorial collaboration with ATLAS and OpenAI ChatGPT; repository publication assisted by OpenAI Codex. Forgotten Industries, YYYY-MM-DD.</p>
      <p>When system or model details are unknown, only the verified product or operating-layer name is cited. Model versions are never inferred.</p>
      <p class="entry-note">The former source route remains available at <a href="/docs/ai-generation-citation-standard.md">/docs/ai-generation-citation-standard.md</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

